  "lyrics": [
    {
      "time": 7.79,
      "time_str": "00:07.790",
      "text": "What I want, you've got and it might be hard to handle",
      "translation": "你有的是我想要的，它似乎很棘手"
    },
    {
      "time": 16.21,
      "time_str": "00:16.210",
      "text": "But like the flame that burns the candle",
      "translation": "但就如燃烧蜡烛的火苗"
    },
    {
      "time": 19.13,
      "time_str": "00:19.130",
      "text": "The candle feeds the flame.",
      "translation": "烛油供给着焰火"
    },
    {
      "time": 23.12,
      "time_str": "00:23.120",
      "text": "What I've got's full stock of thoughts",
      "translation": "我有的是满脑子的奇思妙想"
    },
    {
      "time": 26.8,
      "time_str": "00:26.800",
      "text": "And dreams that scatter",
      "translation": "所有支离破碎的梦想"
    },
    {
      "time": 30.23,
      "time_str": "00:30.230",
      "text": "And you pull them all together",
      "translation": "你将他们一一拼凑"
    },
    {
      "time": 31.7,
      "time_str": "00:31.700",
      "text": "And how, I can't explain.",
      "translation": "缘何，我也未知"
    },
    {
      "time": 35.88,
      "time_str": "00:35.880",
      "text": "But you, you make my dreams come true.",
      "translation": "但你，使我美梦成真"
    },
    {
      "time": 42.77,
      "time_str": "00:42.770",
      "text": "Oh you, you make my dreams come true.",
      "translation": "哦，你实现了我的梦想"
    },
    {
      "time": 57.47,
      "time_str": "00:57.470",
      "text": "On a night when bad",
      "translation": "在一个糟糕的夜晚"
    },
    {
      "time": 60.56,
      "time_str": "01:00.560",
      "text": "Dreams become a screamer,",
      "translation": "美梦成了梦魇"
    },
    {
      "time": 62.82,
      "time_str": "01:02.820",
      "text": "When they're messin' with the dreamer",
      "translation": "当它们干扰着梦中人"
    },
    {
      "time": 65.95,
      "time_str": "01:05.950",
      "text": "I can laugh it in the face.",
      "translation": "我脸上笑着"
    },
    {
      "time": 68.72,
      "time_str": "01:08.720",
      "text": "Twist and shout my way out",
      "translation": "扭动身躯，大声疾呼"
    },
    {
      "time": 72.16,
      "time_str": "01:12.160",
      "text": "And wrap yourself around me",
      "translation": "我紧拥你入怀"
    },
    {
      "time": 74.55,
      "time_str": "01:14.550",
      "text": "'Cause I ain't the way you found me",
      "translation": "因为你不能那样找到我"
    },
    {
      "time": 77.45,
      "time_str": "01:17.450",
      "text": "And I'll never be the same",
      "translation": "我将不再如此"
    },
    {
      "time": 81.18,
      "time_str": "01:21.180",
      "text": "But you, you make my dreams come true.",
      "translation": "但你，让我美梦成真"
    },
    {
      "time": 90.35,
      "time_str": "01:30.350",
      "text": "Oh you, you make my dreams come true.",
      "translation": "哦，你实现了我的梦想"
    },
    {
      "time": 103.22,
      "time_str": "01:43.220",
      "text": "I'm down on the daydream",
      "translation": "我正陷入白日梦中"
    },
    {
      "time": 121.15,
      "time_str": "02:01.150",
      "text": "That sleepwalk should be over by now.",
      "translation": "到现在梦游应该结束了"
    },
    {
      "time": 125.17,
      "time_str": "02:05.170",
      "text": "I know that you, you make my dreams come true.",
      "translation": "我深谙，你使我美梦成真"
    },
    {
